\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0 Once upon a time, there was a young woman named Azola. She was beautiful, kind-hearted, and had a great sense of humor. She lived a simple life, working as a nurse in a local hospital and helping care for her aging grandmother. She had a few close friends, but otherwise kept to herself.}}\par
