\pard\nowidctlpar {{\cf0\f0 But then, things started to change. Banda became more distant, and Azola noticed that he was spending a lot of time with a new friend named Mark. Mark was outgoing and seemed to have a way of getting Banda to do things he normally wouldn\uc0{\u8217}t. Despite her reservations, Azola trusted Banda and didn\uc0{\u8217}t think much of it.}}\par
